    "x": 12, 
    "y": "hey",
    "z": "red"
}, {
    "x": 12, 
    "y": "arnold",
    "z": "black"
}, {
    "x": 12, 
    "y": "hey",
    "z": "red"
}]; 
```

With deep equality comparison it could be done like this: 

``` js
var uniqueData = _.uniq(data); 
